"title": "8475: self-denial",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8475: self-denial",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The willingness to deny oneself possessions or status, in order to grow in holiness and commitment to God. This practice is commended and illustrated by Jesus Christ himself, and underlies Christian fellowship within the church.</p>\n<h2>The wisdom of self-denial</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:20-Prov23:21\">PRO 23:20–23:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:16\">PRO 25:16</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of self-denial in order to put God first</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:8\">DAN 1:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:25\">HEB 11:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:29\">LEV 23:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer35:6\">JER 35:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:3\">DAN 10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:15\">LUK 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:33\">LUK 7:33</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:18\">MAT 11:18</a></p>\n<h2>Self-denial is a requirement of following Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24\">MAT 16:24</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34\">MRK 8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23\">LUK 9:23</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:13\">ACT 21:13</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:7\">PHP 3:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:11\">1PE 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:29\">MAT 5:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:10\">MAT 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:9\">MAT 9:9</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:13-Mark2:14\">MRK 2:13–2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:27-Luke5:28\">LUK 5:27–5:28</a> <em>the calling of Matthew</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:37-Matt10:38\">MAT 10:37–10:38</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:26-Luke14:27\">LUK 14:26–14:27</a> <em>the cost of being a disciple</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:8\">MAT 18:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:43\">MRK 9:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21\">MAT 19:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:22\">LUK 18:22</a> <em>the rich young man</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:27\">MAT 19:27</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:28\">MRK 10:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:28\">LUK 18:28</a> <em>Peter left everything to follow Jesus Christ</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:29-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:29–10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:29-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:29–18:30</a> <em>the rewards of self-denial for the sake of the gospel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:11\">LUK 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:33\">LUK 14:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:34\">LUK 21:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:24\">ACT 20:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:2\">ROM 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:6\">ROM 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:11\">ROM 6:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:13\">ROM 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:14\">ROM 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:12\">1CO 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:25-1Cor9:27\">1CO 9:25–9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:5\">2CO 8:5</a> <em>the example of the Macedonian churches</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20\">GAL 2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16\">GAL 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:23\">GAL 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:3\">COL 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:5\">COL 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:21\">2TI 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:12-Titus2:13\">TIT 2:12–2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:7\">JAS 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:2\">1PE 4:2</a></p>\n<h2>Self-denial for the sake of others</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:11\">RUT 2:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:4\">PHP 2:4</a></strong> <em>Esther put her own life at risk for the sake of her people</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:32\">EXO 32:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:16\">EST 4:16</a>ROM <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth14:21\">14:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:1\">ROM 15:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:13\">1CO 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:23\">1CO 9:23</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:24\">1CO 10:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:33\">1CO 10:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:15\">1CO 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:2\">EPH 4:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:21\">EPH 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:17\">PHP 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:20-Phil2:21\">PHP 2:20–2:21</a> <em>the example of Timothy</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:24\">COL 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:10\">2TI 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:2\">TIT 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:8\">1PE 3:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:5\">1PE 5:5</a></p>\n<h2>Self-denial and the example of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:39\">MAT 26:39</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:36\">MRK 14:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42\">LUK 22:42</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:9\">2CO 8:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:7\">PSA 40:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:7\">ISA 53:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:29\">MAT 11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:1-John13:17\">JHN 13:1–13:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:3\">ROM 15:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1-Eph5:2\">EPH 5:1–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5-Phil2:8\">PHP 2:5–2:8</a></p>",
